*Desi* se da nema hrane u kući. (It happened that there was no food in the house.)

*Desila* se neverovatna stvar. (An incredible thing happened.)

Kad smo se spustili niz brdo, *desilo* se nešto strašno. (When we went down the hill, something terrible happened.)

*Desila* se nesreća, ali srećom niko nije povređen. (An accident happened, but luckily no one was hurt.)

Niko nije očekivao da će se tako nešto *desiti*. (Nobody expected something like that to happen.)

Kad je počela da pada kiša, *desio* se čudo. (When it started raining, a miracle happened.)